textAfterTable: I liked Alpha Protocol (except for the quickly forced to choose dialog). I bought it for like $2 on a Steam sale because it got such bad word of mouth. I would have easily paid $20 or $30 for i, after playing it. I didn't run into anything game-stopping, bugwise, either. I guess I was lucky. So, from my perspective... it's nowhere near as bad as everyone says, IMO.           Date
